V(UKfaculty)$size <- 1.5*sqrt(strength(UKfaculty))
V(UKfaculty)$size2 <- V(UKfaculty)$size * .02
E(UKfaculty)$width <- E(UKfaculty)$weight
G1 <- E(UKfaculty)[weight==1]
G2 <- E(UKfaculty)[weight==2]
E(UKfaculty)[ G1 %--% G1 ]$color <- "pink"
E(UKfaculty)[ G2 %--% G2 ]$color <- "lightblue"
E(UKfaculty)[ G1 %--% G2 ]$color <- "yellow"
V(UKfaculty)$label.dist <-
ifelse(V(UKfaculty)$size >= 1, 0, 1)
plot(UKfaculty, layout=A)

colors = brewer.pal(4, "Dark2")

     vertex.color = V(UKfaculty)$color, vertex.frame.color = NA,
     vertex.label = NA,vertex.shape = 'circle',
     vertex.size = 7, edge.arrow.size = 0.8, edge.curved = TRUE,
